data.description:
Congratulations you just found your dream home which is conveniently located and near Texas Live, AT&T Stadium and Texas Rangers Globe Life Field Stadium. This dream home has not 3 nor 4 but 5 bedrooms with 3 full baths. The home features Large bedrooms with walk-in closets. Bedroom down is great for allowing parents privacy and peace away from the kids. Outdoor patio and Upstairs balcony.  It includes a duel side fireplace between two large living spaces, an open layout. The spacious kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steal appliances, wine cooler, and wet bar. The downstairs bedroom or extra living spaces could also serve as an office area. There are large vaulted ceilings in the upstairs bedrooms, and primary bath includes a separate shower and jetted tub. A relaxing and large back courtyard. Additionally, the home includes a 2 car garage.
BRAND NEW AUG 2021: ROOF & HVAC!
